# Multimodal AI Production Pipeline

A structured skill for architecting end-to-end AI content campaigns using the **7-Step Multimodal Cascade**. All assets are anchored to a centralized Brand Manifest to prevent creative drift across pipeline stages.

---

## Core Architecture: The 7-Step Cascade

| Step | Function | Key Tools | Output Spec |
|------|----------|-----------|-------------|
| 1. Strategy | Brand manifest, psychographics, positioning | Claude/GPT → Brand Manifest | Markdown doc: tone, HEX colors, lens configs, emotional anchor |
| 2. Copywriting | Psychological scripting, voiceover, screen text | GPT/Claude → Script | Script with punctuation-injection formatting |
| 3. Image Generation | Frame 1 hero asset creation | Flux Pro / Midjourney v6.5 + Style Anchor Block | Ultra-high-res .png (≤35% subject occupancy) |
| 4. Video Generation | Image-to-video motion synthesis | Kling 3.0 / Veo 3.1 | 4K .mp4 blocks at locked framerate |
| 5. Voiceover Production | Synthetic voice generation | ElevenLabs + pre-cleansed dataset | Clean .wav with inhalation/vocal fry |
| 6. Soundtrack Composition | Background score | Udio + Step 1 meta-tags | High-fidelity mixed track with 1kHz–3kHz pocket for voiceover |
| 7. Assembly & Automation | Final conform & deployment | Cowork/Remotion/NLE + Brand LUT | Multi-platform output |

> **Downstream Editing Fallacy**: Never patch problems downstream. If Step 4 looks wrong, go back to Step 3 (or Step 2). Fix the source data state, not the symptom.

