## Universal Prompt Validation Checklist

Run before every render:

- [ ] `[State]` clause is static/anchored (no motion implied)
- [ ] `[Subject Motion]` verbs are physical/explicit (no vagueness)
- [ ] `[Camera Motion]` terms are cinematic/technical (no amateur directives)
- [ ] `[Guardrails]` include temporal consistency keywords
- [ ] Style Anchor Block injected verbatim (checksum-verified)
- [ ] `[Audio Specification]` block: foley-only for single-pass
- [ ] Punctuation scripting applied to all voiceover copy
- [ ] Meta-tag structure used for music prompts (bracketed, not conversational)
- [ ] Music prompt ≤4 instrument layers
- [ ] Side-chain compression spec included in Udio prompt

